Best next upgrade

The strongest v3 move is to add problem-type clustering instead of the simple signature buckets.

That means:
	•	not just U0.5_I1.0_C0.0...
	•	but actual learned families like:
	•	strategy problems
	•	writing problems
	•	architecture problems
	•	truth-checking problems
	•	monetization decisions

That would make the depth learning meaningfully smarter.